      "span_text": "An important implication of [CITATION_1] is that aggregate behaviour is not just a function of averages, e.g. a shock that increases the balance sheets of some firms (oil exporters) but decreases that of other firms (oil importers) in the same amount will have an adverse effect on aggregate demand and supply."
